    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年9月22日-2025年9月26日）",
    "followRuleId": "1287697712090845184",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1287371769056989184\">《京东开放平台五星店铺规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①认证范围剔除卖场店；②调整透标期间取消五星店铺标签展示指标；③调整五星店铺认证标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288478539486871552\">《京东开放平台经营类目规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修订补充类目选择规范、类目发品阈值、类目变更、类目错挂处置等规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288761542125641728\">《京东开放平台医药和医疗保健类商品管理规则》</a>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修订细化商品发布信息等要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1287652748564762624\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11活动总则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①活动节奏：预热时间为2025年10月9日00:00:00-2025年10月9日19:59:59；正式时间为2025年10月9日20:00:00-2025年11月14日23:59:59；招商时间为2025年9月23日12:00:00-2025年11月14日23:59:59；②活动玩法：官方直降和跨店满减。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span></strong><span style=\"color: #1400ff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1287649847893168128\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11大促主题活动招商规则》</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、<a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288845533797310464\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11大促官方直降活动规则》</a>、<a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1288840126126465024\">《2025年京东开放平台11.11大促跨店满减活动规则》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285469207579987968\">《京东开放平台大闸蟹商品管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整商品发布、礼券版面信息、商品抽检、违规处理等方面要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1286252501955383296\">《京东开放平台发货管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①延迟发货场景增加订单超7天仍未发货叠加扣除违约金处置规则；②删除错件场景相关规则描述； ③将虚假发货、虚假轨迹、欺诈发货并入发货异常场景中，同时增加&ldquo;延长自动确认收货时间&rdquo;的处置手段。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1286254013129560064\">《京东开放平台个人/个体交易管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285469207579987968\">《京东开放平台兑换无忧服务规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整赔付标准为赔偿实付金额的30%。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285469207579987968\">《京东开放平台生鲜大闸蟹售后赔付管理规范》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整足斤足两赔付标准和卡券价保规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285485775084982272\">《京东开放平台不符合类目发品规则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">将原《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》中1.1类目乱挂相关规则内容删除，类目乱挂相关规则内容迁移到本规则中。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285500712792494080\">《京东开放平台发布禁限售品牌管理细则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确禁售品牌和限售品牌的定义及范围，同时明确禁限售品牌违规定义及处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285512802500481024\">《京东开放平台扰乱经营秩序细则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①对扰乱经营秩序的场景进行调整，对不同场景细化违规定义及对应处理措施；②对违规场景增加规则解读，包括常见违规示例等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285565584804810752\">《京东开放平台发布违规宣传信息细则》&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①增加AI假图、其他不符合实际情况的违规场景；②补充违规场景的规则解读。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">9</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1284795317920862208\">《京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范-违反国家行政法规禁止销售的商品及服务实施细则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">细化违反国家行政法规禁止销售的商品及服务类场景定义，同时对商家易出现的违规问题进行示例描述。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">10</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1284748071690964992\">《京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范-涉及欺诈、作弊、赌博等非法所得及非法用途类实施细则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">细化涉及欺诈、作弊、赌博等非法所得及非法用途类场景定义，同时对商家易出现的违规问题进行示例描述。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">11</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增<span style=\"color: #000000;\">】</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1285435808953798656\">《京东开放平台健康检验检测商家管理规则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确医学检验实验室服务行为规范。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">12</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订<span style=\"color: #000000;\">】</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1400ff;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1284830797156716544\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《&ldquo;京东JD.COM&rdquo;开放平台在线服务协议 》</a> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对争议解决方式进行变更。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; fo